WEBVTT

01:28.088 --> 01:29.255
Why are you so surprised?

01:30.799 --> 01:31.925
Oh, it's nothing.

01:35.095 --> 01:36.387
Can you wait for me outside?

01:36.471 --> 01:38.556
Let me wrap things up here.

01:39.808 --> 01:40.642
Sure.

01:59.119 --> 02:02.205
EPISODE 4

02:52.463 --> 02:54.215
I'm surprised.
What brings you here?

02:55.550 --> 02:57.093
I thought I'd return the favor.

02:59.512 --> 03:00.847
Is there a lot left to do?

03:01.222 --> 03:03.224
I'll pack up my bag and be right down.

03:03.808 --> 03:05.059
I'll bring the car around.

03:05.643 --> 03:06.519
Sure.

03:20.617 --> 03:21.618
Hello?

03:24.579 --> 03:25.705
Where are you?

03:26.414 --> 03:27.540
I left the library.

03:27.790 --> 03:29.000
Didn't you see my text?

03:29.292 --> 03:31.377
Why didn't you reply?
Is this a habit of yours?

03:35.173 --> 03:36.174
Did you...

03:36.716 --> 03:37.800
I saw him.

03:42.096 --> 03:44.891
So what? Why did you hide?

03:45.391 --> 03:48.394
We didn't even do anything.

03:48.770 --> 03:50.063
Would you if I asked you to?

03:54.859 --> 03:56.236
Would you be willing to do it?

03:57.779 --> 03:58.947
Ji-ho.

04:00.490 --> 04:01.741
I said from the start

04:02.533 --> 04:04.577
that I couldn't be just friends with you.

04:04.953 --> 04:06.329
You said you moved on,

04:06.913 --> 04:08.414
so we agreed to be friends.

04:10.375 --> 04:12.252
Then tell Gi-seok that we're friends.

04:13.419 --> 04:17.006
Tell him not to worry when he sees
us together, or should I tell him?

04:18.591 --> 04:19.717
Where are you?

04:24.055 --> 04:25.181
Where?

04:25.515 --> 04:26.975
Let's talk in person.

04:30.561 --> 04:31.813
Where are you?

04:33.815 --> 04:35.149
If you come to me now,

04:37.277 --> 04:38.861
there's no going back.

07:11.013 --> 07:11.973
Isn't that Ji-ho?

07:13.808 --> 07:14.642
Ji-ho!

07:22.024 --> 07:22.859
Hey.

07:27.405 --> 07:28.406
Go ahead.

07:36.122 --> 07:37.081
Unbelievable.

07:38.583 --> 07:39.792
That was unexpected.

07:47.550 --> 07:51.179
Did I mention where you worked
when we met him?

07:53.764 --> 07:55.391
I'm not sure. I don't remember.

07:58.102 --> 08:00.188
I should tell him when we meet again...

08:01.397 --> 08:04.192
and ask him to bring you some snacks.

08:05.735 --> 08:07.028
What if it brings us closer?

08:07.570 --> 08:09.697
He's a friend, so that'd be great.

08:13.659 --> 08:16.662
Are you okay with me spending time
with another guy?

08:19.332 --> 08:21.292
- As a man?
- As a friend.

08:22.627 --> 08:23.920
Just a guy friend.

08:26.214 --> 08:28.466
Would that be okay with you?

08:29.926 --> 08:31.469
Do you even care?

08:33.679 --> 08:36.766
You hate it when people
invade your personal space.

08:39.894 --> 08:41.395
I'm selfish, aren't I?

08:42.146 --> 08:43.773
We wouldn't have dated if you were.

08:46.692 --> 08:48.236
You have a strong personality...

08:49.403 --> 08:51.364
and it's why I fell for you.

08:55.493 --> 08:58.329
Have you ever regretted... dating me?

08:59.205 --> 09:00.498
I nearly did just now...

09:01.666 --> 09:03.334
because of these silly questions.

09:07.338 --> 09:08.214
Gi-seok.

09:08.839 --> 09:09.674
Yes?

09:13.177 --> 09:15.137
Shall we just get married?

09:16.055 --> 09:20.017
I'd like a proper proposal
and not a reluctant one.

09:26.566 --> 09:28.818
I told you not to stress out about it.

09:30.194 --> 09:33.072
We'll get married eventually,
so what's the rush?

09:34.991 --> 09:36.033
Right?

09:48.462 --> 09:54.260
CIVIL SERVICE EXAM CLASSES
CONSULTATIONS WELCOME

09:54.552 --> 09:55.595
Hi.

09:56.345 --> 09:58.973
Yes? I mean, hi.

09:59.307 --> 10:01.601
Did you forget that we're friends?

10:05.896 --> 10:09.317
You appeared out of the blue,
so of course I was flustered.

10:09.400 --> 10:10.985
Did you study a lot today?

10:11.569 --> 10:12.945
I'm not done for the day.

10:13.279 --> 10:15.823
What's with the bag then?
I thought we were going out.

10:16.532 --> 10:18.242
It's a force of habit.

10:18.826 --> 10:20.620
So are we going out or what?

10:22.038 --> 10:23.247
What are we going to do?

10:24.206 --> 10:27.543
We'll think about it over a meal.

10:27.710 --> 10:30.254
- Come on. I'll treat you to barbecue.
- But--

10:30.338 --> 10:31.756
- Let's go!
- Sure.

10:37.678 --> 10:39.472
PREMIUM VITAMIN

10:40.473 --> 10:41.474
Hold on.

10:42.308 --> 10:44.894
Did you really buy all these for me?

10:45.019 --> 10:45.895
No...

10:46.687 --> 10:48.272
They were around the house.

10:48.564 --> 10:50.858
Besides, a hardworking student
needs vitamins more.

10:50.941 --> 10:52.526
No one in my house needs them.

10:53.152 --> 10:56.906
My pharmacist friend
sometimes brings me some,

10:56.989 --> 10:58.616
but never this much.

10:59.367 --> 11:02.620
You won't run out then.
Now, will you dig in?

11:02.787 --> 11:04.372
Oh, right. Thank you.

11:04.872 --> 11:06.290
Thanks for this.

11:07.041 --> 11:08.084
Gosh.

11:12.755 --> 11:14.090
- So...
- Yes?

11:14.382 --> 11:16.801
- How many times did you flunk?
- The exam?

11:17.301 --> 11:18.803
Well, maybe...

11:23.432 --> 11:24.600
So five times?

11:28.813 --> 11:29.897
You're adorable.

11:31.273 --> 11:34.235
A greater number of people
fail the test anyway,

11:34.318 --> 11:36.153
so why be embarrassed about it?

11:36.487 --> 11:38.030
It's not something to be proud of.

11:40.366 --> 11:41.200
So...

11:44.286 --> 11:45.204
It's nothing.

11:45.788 --> 11:47.581
- Why do I keep coming by?
- Yes.

11:47.665 --> 11:48.874
Because I want to see you.

11:50.584 --> 11:53.671
You constantly miss those you're fond of.

11:55.005 --> 11:59.009
How do you know
if I'm a decent person or not?

11:59.093 --> 12:00.469
I'm just drawn to you.

12:04.098 --> 12:08.477
We can take our time
getting to know each other anyway.

12:08.894 --> 12:09.729
Simple, right?

12:10.229 --> 12:11.063
Now eat up.

12:11.564 --> 12:14.191
Are you always this bold?

12:18.696 --> 12:20.656
I'm a bit influenced by Jeong-in.

12:22.032 --> 12:24.285
- Remember my sister?
- Yes.

12:24.785 --> 12:28.080
Well, she always has to
see matters through till the end.

12:28.164 --> 12:29.415
Ma'am, can I get some more?

12:29.498 --> 12:31.917
When she's set on something
that she really wants,

12:32.001 --> 12:33.753
no one in our family can stop her.

12:34.545 --> 12:35.963
She doesn't seem like the type.

12:37.047 --> 12:40.134
She's gotten boring.
That's why her love life sucks, too.

12:40.217 --> 12:43.095
She and Gi-seok look nice together.

12:45.681 --> 12:46.515
What about us?

12:50.478 --> 12:51.562
Unbelievable.

12:53.063 --> 12:55.357
- Eat up. I'll get you some more.
- Right.

12:55.441 --> 12:56.275
Dig in.

12:57.735 --> 12:59.069
- Grill these for me.
- Sure.

13:01.655 --> 13:03.824
"What if I can never take this off?

13:04.200 --> 13:06.076
Will I be stuck like this forever?

13:06.869 --> 13:09.455
Thankfully,
I can somewhat see through this,

13:09.705 --> 13:11.540
so it's not so bad."

13:20.466 --> 13:21.801
He just fell asleep.

13:51.080 --> 13:53.123
- Mom didn't call?
- She did.

13:53.624 --> 13:56.043
They moved to a nearby karaoke room.

13:57.127 --> 13:59.713
You know how the neighbors like to party.

14:00.381 --> 14:01.549
Go before it gets darker.

14:03.259 --> 14:04.718
Want to grab a drink with me?

14:21.360 --> 14:23.946
- You should open a new bottle.
- It's fine.

14:53.726 --> 14:54.977
There's nothing going on.

15:17.625 --> 15:19.001
Should I go up with you?

15:19.835 --> 15:21.670
I thought you had a meeting to prep for.

15:22.463 --> 15:23.547
I do, but...

15:24.882 --> 15:26.258
Come inside if you want.

15:27.718 --> 15:28.886
Where's Jae-in?

15:29.803 --> 15:31.722
She texted that she just got home.

15:34.934 --> 15:36.185
I'm good then.

15:41.941 --> 15:43.400
Jae-in's home, so...

15:46.570 --> 15:47.404
What?

15:50.282 --> 15:52.785
Am I just a regular sexual partner to you?

15:54.703 --> 15:56.288
Did you have to say it like that?

15:57.998 --> 16:00.250
- When have I ever treated you that way?
- Just now.

16:01.669 --> 16:03.754
What's up with you again?

16:04.672 --> 16:06.423
Are you picking fights on purpose?

16:08.801 --> 16:12.137
Besides, couples don't need
to seek permission for sex.

16:13.222 --> 16:15.849
You still need to ask though.

16:15.933 --> 16:18.018
Just say you don't want to

16:18.602 --> 16:20.354
instead of making ridiculous excuses.

16:20.437 --> 16:23.148
I don't want to. Satisfied?

16:28.153 --> 16:29.488
Unbelievable.

16:34.159 --> 16:35.244
Drive home safely.

17:09.653 --> 17:12.239
While raising you,

17:14.158 --> 17:17.286
we got scared every time

17:17.953 --> 17:19.204
a call came from...

17:21.081 --> 17:22.541
your teachers at school.

17:25.586 --> 17:26.962
"Ji-ho...

17:28.630 --> 17:30.674
is at the top of the class again."

17:31.759 --> 17:34.470
"Ji-ho should compete
in an academic competition."

17:38.557 --> 17:40.601
"How about
a foreign language high school?"

17:42.644 --> 17:46.190
"He could get into a university
on a full scholarship."

17:55.741 --> 17:57.910
Your mom and I aren't highly educated,

18:00.913 --> 18:03.248
and we were focused on just getting by.

18:04.041 --> 18:06.668
Why are you suddenly saying this?

18:09.630 --> 18:11.423
We couldn't give you anything,

18:16.762 --> 18:20.474
so I wonder if that's why your life
turned out this way.

18:22.226 --> 18:23.102
What about Eun-u?

18:28.982 --> 18:31.318
For whatever reason, he was sent to me.

18:33.112 --> 18:36.073
I wouldn't change him even if I could.

18:48.377 --> 18:49.336
Dad.

18:53.966 --> 18:55.509
I'm doing fine.

18:56.009 --> 18:58.137
You and Mom raised me well.

18:59.763 --> 19:02.182
So don't worry about me or Eun-u.

19:04.059 --> 19:05.060
I...

19:07.729 --> 19:09.565
I'll raise him well, too.

19:44.933 --> 19:46.226
Hi, Jeong-in.

19:46.852 --> 19:47.895
Seo-in.

19:49.396 --> 19:51.648
What's with your voice? Are you all right?

19:52.065 --> 19:53.066
I'm good.

19:54.443 --> 19:55.861
How are things with you?

19:56.028 --> 19:58.906
I'm fine, but you don't seem that way.

19:59.114 --> 20:00.949
What's going on?

20:03.160 --> 20:03.994
Seo-in.

20:05.454 --> 20:06.288
Yes?

20:07.623 --> 20:09.666
I shouldn't betray...

20:11.501 --> 20:12.628
Gi-seok, right?

20:15.589 --> 20:17.716
I can't turn my back on him now...

20:19.176 --> 20:20.093
right?

20:21.929 --> 20:24.598
If you do,
I'm sure you'd have a good reason.

20:25.182 --> 20:26.725
One that is solid.

20:31.605 --> 20:32.606
Jeong-in.

20:37.903 --> 20:38.737
Yes?

20:40.906 --> 20:43.617
I only want you to think about one thing.

20:45.202 --> 20:46.328
Your happiness.

20:51.959 --> 20:54.336
I want you to be happy too.

20:57.756 --> 20:59.716
There's another man, isn't there?

21:06.056 --> 21:07.099
Jeong-in.

21:10.644 --> 21:12.396
No, that's not it.

21:13.230 --> 21:15.941
I called because
I wanted to hear your voice.

21:17.526 --> 21:19.152
But I'm just talking nonsense...

21:22.990 --> 21:25.701
You're pretending to be all right again.

21:27.619 --> 21:28.870
Look who's talking.

21:31.164 --> 21:32.833
I'm your copycat, remember?

21:35.252 --> 21:36.670
We can get through this.

21:49.433 --> 21:51.101
The file you told me to review

21:51.351 --> 21:53.520
keeps getting classified
as a high-risk loan.

21:55.439 --> 21:56.481
How so?

21:56.648 --> 22:00.110
There isn't a proper file
regarding proof of income

22:00.569 --> 22:02.696
and he's taken out many other loans.

22:03.196 --> 22:04.573
He's in a pile of debt.

22:06.825 --> 22:08.035
I see that he's a dentist.

22:09.328 --> 22:11.413
I don't know how you know this guy,

22:11.496 --> 22:14.291
but you shouldn't approve this loan
even if he's family.

22:15.375 --> 22:16.501
Got it.

22:17.336 --> 22:18.170
Thanks for this.

22:20.756 --> 22:21.590
By the way,

22:21.673 --> 22:23.258
don't miss next week's game.

22:23.759 --> 22:25.594
We need to crush Ji-ho this time.

22:26.511 --> 22:29.514
I thought you'd bring us victory,
but we lost again.

22:29.639 --> 22:30.724
It was humiliating.

22:30.807 --> 22:33.310
I only went soft
because it was my first game.

22:33.602 --> 22:35.395
Just wait. I'll crush him next time.

22:44.696 --> 22:46.239
Unbelievable.

22:46.698 --> 22:47.741
- Su-jin.
- Yes?

22:47.824 --> 22:49.451
This is for a book review event.

22:49.534 --> 22:51.411
Put it at waist-level
so the kids see it.

22:51.495 --> 22:53.580
Sure. Should I put one up
at the annex, too,

22:53.663 --> 22:54.790
where they take classes?

22:54.873 --> 22:57.000
Yes. Make sure
it doesn't overlap other notices.

22:57.084 --> 22:58.001
Right.

23:00.212 --> 23:01.213
Hold on.

23:01.713 --> 23:04.007
Ha-rin and I will cover
the main reference library.

23:04.091 --> 23:06.385
You can manage
the children's library alone, right?

23:06.468 --> 23:08.345
- Ha-rin. Let's do this together.
- Sure.

23:10.305 --> 23:12.516
I'll go with Ha-rin. Come on.

23:25.028 --> 23:26.363
Is something going on?

23:28.490 --> 23:29.324
Well...

23:29.408 --> 23:31.660
you've seemed down
these past few days.

23:33.495 --> 23:34.996
I'm fine. Why do you ask?

23:35.080 --> 23:36.415
You're not fine.

23:38.250 --> 23:40.001
I told you before...

23:41.586 --> 23:43.713
that I'm not the adventurous type.

23:46.341 --> 23:49.010
I thought you meant
you don't like taking risks.

23:50.887 --> 23:52.472
Just how far...

23:54.057 --> 23:55.809
should one go, though?

23:59.187 --> 24:01.440
Should you take risks in life...

24:02.774 --> 24:04.025
or shouldn't you?

24:05.026 --> 24:07.279
It's no big deal,

24:07.779 --> 24:11.491
but Eun-u wanted to go
to the library after kindergarten

24:12.367 --> 24:14.327
and we went to one in the neighborhood.

24:14.536 --> 24:16.371
Apparently, it's not where you took him.

24:16.455 --> 24:17.622
Just a second.

24:18.498 --> 24:20.584
Eun-u, your dad's on the phone.

24:20.667 --> 24:21.918
Hello?

24:22.711 --> 24:25.505
That library has books you like as well.

24:26.214 --> 24:27.257
No!

24:28.383 --> 24:29.468
What do you mean?

24:30.218 --> 24:31.678
This isn't it.

24:34.556 --> 24:37.559
I'll take you to that library next time.

24:38.810 --> 24:39.936
I want to go today.

24:41.480 --> 24:43.648
I told you not to make a fuss
when I'm at work.

24:44.941 --> 24:46.193
I hate you.

24:48.028 --> 24:50.113
You only upset him more.

24:50.655 --> 24:52.115
Where exactly is that library?

24:53.408 --> 24:55.619
It's all right. Just please take him home.

24:56.203 --> 24:59.331
We're already outside,
so tell me where it is.

25:00.373 --> 25:01.917
Just don't.

25:02.626 --> 25:04.920
But Eun-u's throwing a tantrum.

25:05.420 --> 25:07.464
He can't always get what he wants.

25:07.547 --> 25:09.883
Just be strict with him.
I need to go back to work.

25:10.467 --> 25:11.676
I'll call you later.

25:42.290 --> 25:46.127
WOORI PHARMACY

26:17.158 --> 26:19.035
- Hope you enjoy your food.
- Thank you.

29:06.703 --> 29:09.414
Good work today.
That's it for today's class.

29:09.497 --> 29:11.916
- Okay. Thank you.
- Thank you.

29:17.756 --> 29:19.924
You're getting better by the day.

29:21.509 --> 29:24.220
If I hadn't gotten married
at such a young age,

29:24.304 --> 29:26.306
I would've pursued an artistic career.

29:26.473 --> 29:28.141
You can still do it.

29:28.224 --> 29:30.727
It's too late for this lifetime.

29:36.149 --> 29:37.400
Why is he calling me?

29:38.193 --> 29:41.821
Hi, Si-hoon. Yes, what's up?

29:42.781 --> 29:46.034
Everything is fine with us, of course.

29:46.159 --> 29:47.202
Why did you call?

29:47.952 --> 29:48.995
Oh, really?

29:49.913 --> 29:52.415
Sure, by all means. What about Seo-in?

29:55.752 --> 29:57.629
Right. Anyway, okay.

29:57.921 --> 29:59.422
I'll give her a call as well.

30:00.006 --> 30:02.842
All right. Take it easy.

30:04.052 --> 30:05.470
What's gotten into him?

30:06.012 --> 30:06.971
Your son-in-law?

30:07.055 --> 30:10.058
Yes. He wants to come over for dinner
in a few days.

30:17.190 --> 30:18.358
Third floor.

30:20.401 --> 30:21.903
The door is opening.

30:23.988 --> 30:25.073
Going up.

30:29.786 --> 30:31.246
The door is closing.

30:38.211 --> 30:39.546
Why haven't I heard anything?

30:42.048 --> 30:43.550
I'm still thinking about it.

30:44.092 --> 30:45.510
What's there to think about?

30:45.927 --> 30:48.555
You know that
it's a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity.

30:50.098 --> 30:53.643
I'll be hosting it alone,
so there will be a lot of pressure.

30:55.144 --> 30:59.524
Isn't a little bit of pressure essential
when it comes to work?

30:59.858 --> 31:02.110
- The door is opening.
- Don't think too hard.

31:02.819 --> 31:05.280
- Okay. I'll let you know my decision soon.
- Going up.

31:05.864 --> 31:08.241
The decision has already been made
by the higher-ups.

31:08.324 --> 31:09.617
Just make up your mind.

31:13.371 --> 31:15.456
- This opportunity...
- The door is closing.

31:15.540 --> 31:18.001
...will help you generate
a career breakthrough.

31:24.090 --> 31:25.633
The door is closing.

31:30.722 --> 31:33.224
- Is Mr. Kwon--
- Oh, he went to the dentist.

31:33.600 --> 31:35.977
- The dentist?
- That's what he said.

31:36.519 --> 31:37.562
I see.

31:39.063 --> 31:39.898
Okay.

32:12.055 --> 32:15.141
I'm Dr. Nam's father-in-law.
Can I speak to him?

32:16.225 --> 32:18.770
I'll keep it short, so tell him
to step out for a second.

32:18.853 --> 32:20.146
Tell him it's me.

32:20.480 --> 32:21.314
Yes.

32:28.279 --> 32:31.366
Hey, Si-hoon. It's me. You must be busy.

32:34.410 --> 32:36.746
Well, I called because it looks like

32:37.413 --> 32:40.500
the chief director
has an appointment with you today.

32:42.085 --> 32:43.670
Oh, he's not there yet?

32:46.172 --> 32:50.259
Well, could you take
extra good care of him?

32:53.179 --> 32:54.347
All right, sounds good.

32:54.681 --> 32:57.809
It sure is nice to have a son-in-law
who is a dentist.

32:58.726 --> 32:59.936
Yes, get back to work.

33:00.186 --> 33:02.855
One more thing. You see,

33:03.523 --> 33:08.027
you don't need to tell him that I called.

33:08.111 --> 33:09.445
Don't worry.

33:09.988 --> 33:13.032
Yes, we'll take good care of him.
Speak to you soon. Bye.

33:14.701 --> 33:17.537
I told you I can't take any calls
when I'm with patients.

33:17.620 --> 33:18.621
Got it.

33:20.415 --> 33:23.501
A patient named Kwon Yeong-guk
has an appointment today.

33:24.585 --> 33:25.878
- Here.
- He's here.

33:28.631 --> 33:30.717
- Hello.
- Mr. Kwon, how have you been?

33:30.800 --> 33:33.219
- It's been a while.
- I know. Come on in.

33:33.386 --> 33:35.555
I'm a little early.

33:35.638 --> 33:39.058
It's okay. It's for a quick checkup,
so you can come in now.

33:42.812 --> 33:44.188
Have you eaten yet?

33:44.522 --> 33:46.441
- I'm going to eat after this.
- I see.

33:46.899 --> 33:49.569
I actually met up with Gi-seok
for a drink recently.

33:49.986 --> 33:51.112
- Really?
- Yes.

33:52.196 --> 33:55.450
He's been saying he's too busy to see me
since the transfer.

33:56.242 --> 33:59.871
I guess he wanted my advice
on the marriage issue.

34:00.747 --> 34:01.831
What issue?

34:03.082 --> 34:05.293
Well, I'm not saying
they're having problems.

34:05.460 --> 34:08.171
He asked me how he can build
a happy marriage.

34:08.379 --> 34:10.048
We're practically family, you know.

34:11.758 --> 34:13.051
You're a funny man.

34:14.677 --> 34:16.179
What do you mean you're family?

34:18.639 --> 34:21.684
We will be in the near future.
That's what I meant.

34:23.561 --> 34:24.729
Please have a seat.

34:31.360 --> 34:32.779
I'll lower the chair.

34:41.162 --> 34:42.371
Please cover his face.

34:50.713 --> 34:52.757
Something must be up with Ji-ho.

34:52.965 --> 34:55.510
- Is he feeling unwell?
- He's doing that again?

35:06.813 --> 35:08.439
I can see you in the reflection.

35:09.273 --> 35:10.483
And I'm fine.

35:12.944 --> 35:16.030
Do something productive instead of
standing around being all fidgety.

35:16.155 --> 35:19.200
Goodness.
Ye-seul, what's the matter with her?

35:20.201 --> 35:21.661
We're just worried about you.

35:21.786 --> 35:25.123
You've been skipping lunch,
and all you do is look out the window.

35:25.623 --> 35:29.085
I don't have much of an appetite,
and I have a lot on my mind these days.

35:29.919 --> 35:32.130
- It's because of a woman, right?
- Seriously?

35:32.505 --> 35:33.714
No, obviously.

35:33.798 --> 35:34.882
- Why not?
- Why not?

35:35.967 --> 35:38.302
The fact that we said
the same thing simultaneously

35:38.386 --> 35:40.138
proves that you're wrong.

35:40.221 --> 35:43.182
There's no right answer.
People come from all walks of life.

35:43.558 --> 35:46.269
Giving up without even trying
is also a habit.

35:57.238 --> 36:00.032
I've told you
that your life is important too.

36:01.159 --> 36:03.452
I'm telling you
as someone who's been through it.

36:04.620 --> 36:07.248
It's a disservice to yourself
to do something you'd regret.

36:14.213 --> 36:15.381
Get going soon.

36:18.634 --> 36:20.386
- Are you closed?
- No, we're still open.

36:20.469 --> 36:21.512
- Thank you.
- No problem.

36:23.806 --> 36:27.560
I got a deep paper cut.
I put on a bandage for now.

36:28.728 --> 36:29.979
What about ointment--

36:30.062 --> 36:33.024
We also have hydrocolloid bandages
that you can put on the skin.

36:33.107 --> 36:34.609
I'll get the bandage.

36:34.692 --> 36:36.986
There are different sizes.
Just pick what you need.

36:37.069 --> 36:38.029
Okay, thank you.

36:39.280 --> 36:41.449
I heard you and Jeong-in know each other.

36:45.953 --> 36:47.955
I work with her.

36:48.247 --> 36:49.415
- I see.
- Oh, no.

36:50.458 --> 36:51.500
Here you go.

36:59.634 --> 37:00.718
Is Jeong-in...

37:02.094 --> 37:03.262
doing well?

37:04.639 --> 37:05.681
So?

37:06.224 --> 37:08.059
Hey, what do you want to hear?

37:08.434 --> 37:10.102
Is there something going on?

37:10.895 --> 37:11.938
Hey, Yeong-ju.

37:12.271 --> 37:13.981
You'd better be honest with me.

37:14.065 --> 37:17.652
Even last time you talked about him,
I thought it was so odd.

37:19.111 --> 37:20.363
Stop talking nonsense.

37:21.155 --> 37:24.158
By the way, did he say anything else?

37:24.951 --> 37:26.661
Anything else? Like what?

37:27.036 --> 37:29.830
Oh, he asked if you're doing well.
I said you're doing fine.

37:29.914 --> 37:31.249
I asked him why he asked--

37:31.666 --> 37:33.459
Shit! Hold on. Just a second.

37:34.752 --> 37:35.586
What happened?

37:37.129 --> 37:38.130
Hello?

37:39.757 --> 37:40.883
Yeong-ju.

37:41.342 --> 37:42.343
Hello?

37:43.678 --> 37:47.890
Mom, you know...
When you're sending me side dishes...

37:48.391 --> 37:51.060
Yes. The other kind of kimchi...

37:52.103 --> 37:54.605
- and other things--
- Hey, what's happening?

37:54.981 --> 37:56.816
Yes, send me some kimchi.

38:01.487 --> 38:03.531
I forgot for a moment
that he's my neighbor.

38:04.031 --> 38:07.952
I thought he followed me
to the convenience store to ask about you.

38:10.913 --> 38:11.956
Hello?

38:12.540 --> 38:14.417
Finish what you were saying earlier.

38:15.793 --> 38:18.671
What did he say when you asked him
why he was asking about me?

38:20.840 --> 38:23.592
He said, "I was just wondering
if all is well with her."

38:25.678 --> 38:26.846
Why are you all quiet?

38:28.806 --> 38:29.807
Jeong-in.

38:30.975 --> 38:32.101
It's nothing.

38:33.019 --> 38:34.687
By the way, what did he buy?

38:35.104 --> 38:36.731
What did I buy? I picked up--

38:36.856 --> 38:38.399
No, him.

38:39.859 --> 38:43.112
I think he bought some food.
It must've been for dinner.

38:45.823 --> 38:49.827
Hey, what's up with these questions?

38:51.203 --> 38:54.749
Hey, Yeong-ju. Let's talk later.
I have to do something.

38:55.291 --> 38:56.417
All of a sudden?

38:57.501 --> 38:58.544
Okay, fine.

39:12.892 --> 39:16.354
Did you hang out
with Jeong-in's brother-in-law recently?

39:16.771 --> 39:18.606
He told me at his clinic today.

39:21.275 --> 39:24.695
Yes, I met up with him briefly
a little while ago.

39:26.280 --> 39:28.074
You should keep your distance.

39:29.658 --> 39:32.661
Getting too close won't do you any good.

39:34.914 --> 39:36.207
I'll figure it out.

39:37.708 --> 39:39.668
You say that all the time.

39:40.878 --> 39:42.880
What are your interests anyway?

39:43.881 --> 39:46.300
Working to earn enough money to spend

39:46.801 --> 39:50.554
and playing sports with your buddies?
That's all?

39:56.894 --> 39:57.978
Thank you.

40:00.106 --> 40:01.941
- You may leave for the day.
- Yes, sir.

40:03.275 --> 40:04.360
Thank you.

40:10.032 --> 40:13.202
I haven't said anything
and let you date Jeong-in until now,

40:14.620 --> 40:17.373
but it wasn't because I like her.

40:19.083 --> 40:22.253
You stopped talking about
wanting to get back into music

40:22.336 --> 40:24.672
after you started dating her,
so I just let you be.

40:25.589 --> 40:27.883
You seem to have finally gotten
yourself together,

40:29.343 --> 40:31.762
so I think you should end
your relationship with her.

40:35.099 --> 40:36.642
But you've never formally met her.

40:36.725 --> 40:38.352
I don't need to meet her to know.

40:39.854 --> 40:41.814
I told you that marriage is a business.

40:42.064 --> 40:44.400
Try to look at the big picture.

40:44.483 --> 40:49.280
Whatever you say,
I won't break up with her right now.

40:50.823 --> 40:53.492
Don't get too serious with her.

40:54.869 --> 40:56.412
I might marry her.

40:58.539 --> 40:59.832
You fool.

41:03.544 --> 41:04.920
Do you love her to death?

41:07.506 --> 41:09.008
You need the basketball court?

41:12.928 --> 41:13.762
Yes.

41:14.555 --> 41:17.308
I'll let the administration know,
so you can just call them.

41:24.440 --> 41:26.692
- Number One!
- Hey, here!

41:27.860 --> 41:29.236
- Hey!
- Mark him.

41:30.863 --> 41:31.739
- No!
- Hey.

41:32.698 --> 41:35.159
- Move!
- Go, guys! Let's win!

41:35.743 --> 41:36.952
You got this!

41:48.756 --> 41:50.174
One more time!

41:57.389 --> 41:58.766
- You got this!
- Go!

42:02.019 --> 42:02.895
Go for it!

42:07.942 --> 42:08.984
Hey!

43:12.214 --> 43:13.424
Let's go.

43:14.383 --> 43:16.844
Should we have gone
to a proper grocery store?

43:16.927 --> 43:18.053
That way, we can cook.

43:18.387 --> 43:19.930
I'm a better cook than you are.

43:20.598 --> 43:21.724
I don't care who cooks.

43:22.391 --> 43:24.685
I should ask Mom
to bring us some side dishes.

43:25.477 --> 43:27.062
She's probably still mad at me.

43:28.480 --> 43:29.732
Does Mom know you're here?

43:30.316 --> 43:31.567
She found out a while ago.

43:32.610 --> 43:34.194
Right. I told Seo-in, not you.

43:35.988 --> 43:38.073
No wonder I haven't heard from Mom.

43:38.574 --> 43:40.200
You're such a troublemaker!

43:40.409 --> 43:42.036
- "You're such a troublemaker."
- Hey!

43:42.620 --> 43:43.454
I'm sorry.

43:52.171 --> 43:53.255
Seo-in.

43:55.633 --> 43:56.634
Seo-in.

43:57.760 --> 43:58.802
Seo-in?

44:01.680 --> 44:04.808
You said you'd nap for just a few minutes,
but it's been over an hour.

44:04.975 --> 44:06.685
Are you that tired these days?

44:08.103 --> 44:09.855
I haven't been sleeping well.

44:11.065 --> 44:12.274
Is Si-hoon here?

44:12.358 --> 44:14.985
Yes, he rang the buzzer
from the parking lot.

44:15.069 --> 44:16.904
That's why I came in to wake you up.

44:17.780 --> 44:21.700
By the way, where did he have to go
on his day off?

44:22.242 --> 44:24.453
Oh, he said
he had to take care of something.

44:29.291 --> 44:30.334
Why do you ask?

44:31.168 --> 44:32.544
Well, just because.

44:33.462 --> 44:34.755
You could've come together.

44:34.838 --> 44:37.508
You two can't go home together
because you came separately.

44:39.385 --> 44:41.595
- I'll be out in a minute.
- Okay.

45:01.281 --> 45:04.702
You didn't have to get anything.
Why did you buy so many things?

45:04.785 --> 45:06.829
It's nothing, just some
red ginseng and honey.

45:06.912 --> 45:10.124
Take them regularly.
I heard they're good for you.

45:10.916 --> 45:14.336
You didn't have to make all this food.
Thank you, Mother.

45:14.420 --> 45:16.880
No problem at all. Dig in.

45:17.005 --> 45:18.298
Okay, thank you.

45:23.512 --> 45:24.847
How's your clinic doing?

45:24.930 --> 45:26.932
I hear most clinics
aren't doing well lately.

45:27.141 --> 45:29.977
I'm actually thinking of
expanding the clinic.

45:30.936 --> 45:33.188
Do it if you need more space.
How much bigger?

45:33.313 --> 45:36.024
Nothing is concrete yet.
I should start planning.

45:36.942 --> 45:40.446
Location is everything.
Pick an area where rich people live.

45:40.571 --> 45:42.823
The problem
is that those areas are expensive.

45:43.198 --> 45:45.117
Gosh, it shouldn't be
a factor in deciding.

45:45.200 --> 45:47.119
The more you invest, the more you'll earn.

45:47.202 --> 45:49.747
Don't look far for an example.
We have one right here.

45:49.830 --> 45:52.499
She met Si-hoon
after becoming a news anchor, you know.

45:53.751 --> 45:56.420
I could only meet her
because I chose to become a dentist.

45:56.503 --> 45:59.506
I wouldn't have been able to meet
this successful woman otherwise.

46:05.304 --> 46:07.681
Oh, right.
I met up with Gi-seok the other day.

46:07.931 --> 46:08.766
- Really?
- Yes.

46:08.849 --> 46:12.311
He seemed quite stressed out
because of Jeong-in.

46:13.103 --> 46:14.730
Is that right? What did he say?

46:17.900 --> 46:20.152
Why do you keep making him uncomfortable?

46:21.528 --> 46:23.781
I think he wants to marry her
as soon as possible.

46:23.864 --> 46:25.574
He asked me for advice.

46:26.533 --> 46:27.743
And that being said,

46:29.077 --> 46:32.790
I think we should help him out.

46:33.582 --> 46:35.751
You should've told him
to take control.

46:36.293 --> 46:38.670
Jeong-in doesn't really mean
what she says.

46:38.754 --> 46:40.672
He should just take the lead.

46:40.756 --> 46:42.549
Is Jeong-in an obedient dog or what?

46:43.675 --> 46:44.802
I won't ask for a lot.

46:45.803 --> 46:48.597
Can you please be mindful
of the basic manners at least?

46:52.309 --> 46:53.352
Keep this in mind.

46:54.061 --> 46:56.563
If you do to Jeong-in
what you did to me,

46:57.105 --> 46:59.191
you'll lose her for good.

47:03.862 --> 47:05.322
Shouldn't you call her first?

47:05.989 --> 47:08.325
Do you think Mom will answer my call now?

47:08.534 --> 47:10.494
She's mad at me, not you.

47:10.994 --> 47:13.705
She must be so upset with me
for totally fooling her.

47:15.958 --> 47:19.253
What should I get for Mom?
What can make her anger go away?

47:19.711 --> 47:21.797
Whatever you buy,
only Dad will get excited.

47:28.303 --> 47:29.763
Did you take
what was in these?

47:30.806 --> 47:33.267
The vitamins? I gave them to someone.

47:34.351 --> 47:36.603
Who? All of it?

47:37.688 --> 47:38.981
You weren't taking them.

47:39.439 --> 47:40.691
Were you taking them?

47:41.108 --> 47:43.402
Jae-in, should I teach you a lesson?

47:48.198 --> 47:49.825
Is your body feeling okay?

47:50.909 --> 47:52.786
- Oh, thank you.
- Thank you.

47:53.412 --> 47:54.538
Thank you.

47:55.163 --> 47:56.957
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

47:57.040 --> 47:58.792
Here, this one is yours.

47:59.167 --> 48:01.420
- Pass them around.
- Let's drink until we drop.

48:04.256 --> 48:05.757
- Thank you.
- This one is yours.

48:07.134 --> 48:10.137
- Shall we clink our glasses?
- Is the pharmacy open today?

48:11.889 --> 48:13.140
Don't keep me waiting.

48:13.223 --> 48:15.601
- Good work today.
- Well done, everyone.

48:29.781 --> 48:30.908
Yes, we're open.

48:53.430 --> 48:54.640
You should eat though.

48:54.723 --> 48:56.892
- What's going on?
- It sounds like an emergency.

48:58.352 --> 48:59.686
I'll eat when I get home.

49:00.354 --> 49:01.647
Get home safely.

49:02.356 --> 49:03.690
Guys, let's drink.

49:03.774 --> 49:06.443
- Bye.
- Bye.

49:23.126 --> 49:25.587
Why didn't you just say
we're about to get a divorce?

49:26.964 --> 49:28.548
Right. I'm sure you're afraid.

49:28.715 --> 49:31.551
It'll bring disgrace to your perfect life.

49:34.137 --> 49:36.598
You can try to ruin my life all you want.

49:37.307 --> 49:38.725
Just leave my sisters alone.

49:39.226 --> 49:42.646
Hey, what did I do to Jae-in and Jeong-in?

49:42.729 --> 49:45.357
I haven't even spoken to them
for the past year and a half.

49:45.440 --> 49:47.651
Don't act like you don't get
what I'm saying.

49:48.193 --> 49:50.362
Jeong-in can decide
whether she'll get married.

49:50.529 --> 49:54.116
Don't stick your nose into her business
and tell her what to do.

49:54.199 --> 49:55.325
Jeez.

49:56.451 --> 49:59.246
You're acting up like this
because I've been easy on you.

49:59.329 --> 50:01.123
- Come here.
- Let go.

50:01.206 --> 50:02.666
- I said come here.
- Why?

50:02.749 --> 50:04.876
Come here! Jeez.

50:27.107 --> 50:28.358
Gosh.

50:29.317 --> 50:31.820
WOORI PHARMACY

50:39.870 --> 50:41.830
Security deactivated.

51:03.935 --> 51:05.812
Crap. Darn it.

51:25.499 --> 51:28.376
You're off today, right?
What are you up to?

51:50.982 --> 51:53.026
WOORI PHARMACY

51:53.318 --> 51:54.402
You're here.

51:56.029 --> 51:57.989
I guess you couldn't leave because of me.

51:58.573 --> 51:59.908
A customer left just now.

52:01.910 --> 52:03.829
By the way, where's your lab coat?

52:05.080 --> 52:06.623
I was just about to leave.

52:12.003 --> 52:16.174
Those vitamins...
I want to buy them again.

52:17.050 --> 52:18.593
Why? You didn't like them?

52:18.677 --> 52:22.597
It's not that. I misplaced them,
so I need to buy them again.

52:24.766 --> 52:26.184
Which ones specifically?

52:27.269 --> 52:28.562
What was in those bags?

52:30.522 --> 52:31.565
You didn't take any?

52:33.191 --> 52:34.943
I don't like taking pills.

52:36.069 --> 52:38.405
I feel bad saying that to a pharmacist.

52:40.157 --> 52:41.533
I don't like reading books.

52:43.577 --> 52:44.870
You must lack in culture.

52:46.204 --> 52:47.622
You must be nutrient deficient.

52:48.415 --> 52:49.833
I see that you can boast.

52:50.417 --> 52:52.627
I'm better at playing dumb
after scolding people.

52:53.920 --> 52:55.130
You call that "scolding"?

52:56.131 --> 52:57.591
Scolding isn't just spanking.

53:04.139 --> 53:06.224
- Spill.
- It will happen.

53:06.308 --> 53:07.809
- Then it is happening.
- Finally.

53:07.893 --> 53:11.146
Guys, Gi-seok is finally getting hitched.

53:12.063 --> 53:13.523
- Finally!
- Congratulations!

53:14.733 --> 53:17.360
Gi-seok! You did it!

53:17.903 --> 53:20.030
- Don't leave us.
- Not now. We're just planning.

53:20.113 --> 53:23.158
- It's not set in stone yet.
- Either way, you are getting married.

53:23.241 --> 53:25.410
Right, I will. I mean, eventually.

53:25.493 --> 53:26.828
You're living the life.

53:26.912 --> 53:28.955
Don't hog all the good things
for yourself.

53:29.039 --> 53:31.291
- Help us out here. Right, guys?
- Yes, totally.

53:31.374 --> 53:34.169
- Definitely.
- Yes, please. Help us out.

53:35.837 --> 53:36.922
Help us out.

53:37.631 --> 53:39.841
- Help us out, Gi-seok.
- Hey, wait.

53:39.925 --> 53:42.427
Let's put it into action today.

53:42.510 --> 53:43.595
What do you mean?

53:43.845 --> 53:45.639
Tell your girlfriend to join us,

53:46.056 --> 53:48.600
but she has to bring a friend
who's single.

53:49.184 --> 53:50.560
- Good idea, right?
- Great idea.

53:51.061 --> 53:52.395
- Good idea.
- Nice one.

53:52.479 --> 53:54.272
Where did you guys learn these tricks?

53:54.856 --> 53:56.733
Gi-seok, take your phone out.

53:56.816 --> 53:58.401
It's late. I can't call her now.

53:58.944 --> 53:59.986
- Come on.
- It's not...

54:00.070 --> 54:03.073
She's resting at home.
Why bother her at this late hour?

54:03.156 --> 54:04.199
Come on. Help us out.

54:04.282 --> 54:06.076
- Don't you pity us?
- Drink and go home.

54:09.621 --> 54:12.123
Construction rarely happens here.
It's so noisy, right?

54:12.749 --> 54:14.292
I'm leaving soon, so it's okay.

54:43.655 --> 54:44.698
You can go to the back.

54:45.991 --> 54:47.075
Take the call inside.

55:25.864 --> 55:26.990
Hey, were you sleeping?

55:28.033 --> 55:30.118
No. What's up?

55:30.618 --> 55:33.913
Well, I'm out having drinks with the guys,

55:33.997 --> 55:35.665
but they kept asking me to call you.

55:37.250 --> 55:39.294
Jeong-in, come and join us!

55:39.878 --> 55:42.464
- No.
- We're waiting for you.

55:42.547 --> 55:44.591
It sounds like you drank a lot. Go home.

55:44.758 --> 55:46.009
Yes, I should go home soon.

55:48.845 --> 55:51.806
Jeong-in, do you want to join us briefly?

55:52.223 --> 55:54.309
- You're saying it, too?
- Okay, all right.

55:55.352 --> 55:57.937
Then just stay home.
I'll come by in a bit.

55:58.021 --> 55:59.105
No...

56:00.482 --> 56:01.358
don't come.

56:02.150 --> 56:04.778
Hey, let me see you. We need to make up.

56:05.570 --> 56:06.654
Wait for me.

56:08.156 --> 56:09.366
I said, don't come.

56:21.586 --> 56:22.921
It's a hassle for you.

56:23.505 --> 56:27.592
I'LL DRIVE YOU HOME NOW,
SO TELL HIM TO COME

56:29.094 --> 56:30.845
No, I'm listening.

56:59.791 --> 57:00.959
You asked me.

57:03.753 --> 57:05.380
What do you want me to do?

57:06.840 --> 57:07.966
I never asked.

57:09.008 --> 57:10.510
I'll just take a taxi home.

57:11.386 --> 57:12.804
That's not what I'm asking.

57:16.015 --> 57:17.725
You know what I'm talking about.

57:19.769 --> 57:21.187
Do you want me to stop you?

57:30.280 --> 57:32.615
You tell me. What do you want from me?

57:33.658 --> 57:34.993
What do you want me to do?

57:36.286 --> 57:39.080
Should I tell you not to worry
about the fact that I'm taken?

57:42.000 --> 57:43.835
Do you want me to be the only bad one?

57:44.836 --> 57:47.172
Then why did you even come to the library?

57:48.673 --> 57:49.799
I wanted to see you.

57:57.765 --> 57:58.808
I'm...

58:11.321 --> 58:12.405
I'm--

58:36.763 --> 58:38.306
What I want to say is...

01:00:12.400 --> 01:00:13.860
First off, I'm sorry.

01:00:16.195 --> 01:00:17.655
You're right.

01:00:19.324 --> 01:00:21.826
I went there to see you on a whim,
without a plan,

01:00:22.619 --> 01:00:25.371
and I dumped it all on you,
asking you to make a choice,

01:00:27.498 --> 01:00:29.000
so that if anyone asked me,

01:00:30.376 --> 01:00:32.003
I could say, "I didn't do anything.

01:00:33.338 --> 01:00:35.214
I wasn't even interested...

01:00:37.008 --> 01:00:38.593
but Lee Jeong-in seduced me."

01:00:40.720 --> 01:00:42.847
I was looking for such lame excuses.

01:00:48.811 --> 01:00:51.564
In that sense, I'm not any better.

01:00:53.650 --> 01:00:55.318
I pestered you to be my friend,

01:00:56.361 --> 01:00:58.112
and called you when I didn't need to.

01:00:59.864 --> 01:01:03.951
And like today, I came up
with plausible excuses to come see you.

01:01:05.411 --> 01:01:06.704
At this late hour.

01:01:09.999 --> 01:01:11.918
I guess I was lamer after all.

01:01:14.754 --> 01:01:15.922
I'm sorry, too.

01:01:21.135 --> 01:01:23.304
There's nothing I can do for you.

01:01:24.931 --> 01:01:25.973
That's not true.

01:01:28.643 --> 01:01:30.478
I'm so glad...

01:01:32.230 --> 01:01:33.314
I got to know you.

01:01:37.944 --> 01:01:39.237
You're a good person.

01:01:51.416 --> 01:01:52.458
No, I'm not.

01:01:54.335 --> 01:01:56.045
I'm getting bad desires now.

01:01:59.799 --> 01:02:01.884
I won't expect anything from you,

01:02:02.969 --> 01:02:05.012
so just let me see you.

01:02:07.056 --> 01:02:08.474
I promise I won't get caught.

01:02:11.978 --> 01:02:13.396
No, that's not right.

01:02:15.481 --> 01:02:17.191
I understand how you feel, but--

01:02:17.275 --> 01:02:18.401
I'm talking about you.

01:02:22.780 --> 01:02:24.615
I won't get caught by you.

01:03:08.117 --> 01:03:10.536
If we just let ourselves
follow these feelings,

01:03:10.620 --> 01:03:13.080
it'll be much harder for me to stop.

01:03:13.164 --> 01:03:15.750
And things will be a lot harder for you.

01:03:15.833 --> 01:03:18.044
Help me. I need your help, Jeong-in.

01:03:18.127 --> 01:03:20.588
You don't want to get married?
We won't get married.

01:03:20.671 --> 01:03:22.048
I won't bring it up. Happy?

01:03:22.131 --> 01:03:23.382
Do you think I'm an idiot

01:03:23.466 --> 01:03:25.134
because I haven't brought it up?

01:03:25.218 --> 01:03:28.346
Do you really think I wouldn't know
what your parents think about me?

01:03:28.429 --> 01:03:29.764
I'm breaking up with Gi-seok.

01:03:29.847 --> 01:03:33.184
Do you like the pharmacist that much?
Enough to end your relationship?

01:03:33.309 --> 01:03:36.687
The nasty war has begun.

01:03:36.771 --> 01:03:38.147
Your boyfriend won't let you.

01:03:38.231 --> 01:03:39.565
I want to talk. Let's meet.

01:03:39.649 --> 01:03:42.276
- What did you want to talk about?
- Let's break up.

01:03:42.360 --> 01:03:43.319
Did something happen?

01:03:43.402 --> 01:03:45.863
Am I the only one having a hard time?

01:03:45.947 --> 01:03:48.199
- I guess you're fine.
- You shouldn't have come.

01:03:48.282 --> 01:03:50.535
What do you expect me to do
if you show up now...

01:03:52.995 --> 01:03:54.997
Subtitle translation by Hye-lim Park
